high_descs: Turn around and face bath tub
Pick up soap in bath tub
Turn around, walk forward, turn right at sink
Put soap in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up soap
Turn right, walk back to bath tub, turn left, walk forward
Turn left facing toilet, place soap on top of toilet
anns.task_desc: Move soap from bath to sink and finally toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and look at the bath tub.
Pick up the soap in the tub.
Turn around and walk to the closest sink.
Rinse the soap in the sink.
Turn right and walk around the toilet to the other side.
Place the soap on the toilet tank near the center.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Pick up soap from tub, to the left of the dirty cloths.
Turn around until reach first sink on right.  Turn right, go to sink.
Put soap in sink under right faucet, turn on water, turn off water, drain water.
Turn right, proceed to tub, turn left, proceed to toilet.  Turn left to face toilet.
Put soap on back of toilet.
anns.task_desc: Remove soap from tub, wash soap in sink, put soap on back of toilet.
